reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 5, 2023
reviews.reviewText: This was a great upgrade from my cube-styled bookcase. It was easy to put together and get on the wall. The unit looks like it came with my house. It fits perfectly!Beautiful quality. Easy instructions and easy installation.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 17, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Really love this shelf. We used it in my son’s room to display legos. It is a big shelf with lots of space and is sturdy but it does not take up too much room. Definitely recommend.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 25, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Good unit, shelves too shallow for my liking
reviews.reviewText: The shelves were easy to assemble and look pretty good. My only real gripe with the whole thing is that the shelves are just too shallow. They are only 9 inches deep. I saw too many questions or reviews asking about the depth - NINE inches. Really wish they had been 10-12 so some larger items could fit. Other than that, no complaints. Looks nice in the corner.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 11, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect bookshelf for small space
reviews.reviewText: I have a very small townhouse. I needed a bookshelf but a traditional would have looked ridicules. Only one I found that was this small and actually added to the aesthetic of the room.It’s not solid wood or fancy but it does the job and looks good doing it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 12, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great space saving shelf
reviews.reviewText: I got this as a new bookshelf for my sons room and it’s perfect. I love the corner design as it saves a lot of space but also holds a lot of books and other things. The quality of the boards is better than I expected as well. It was a little wobbly after I put it together but that got better once it was secured to the wall.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 24, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Turned out perfect!
reviews.reviewText: I was hesitant this shelf would look cheap when we took it out of the box but it turned out perfect! I love the open shelves (allows us to still access the outlets) and it mounts to the wall therefore my toddles cannot pull it down into them. There is some “wasted” space in the center where the two shelves connect due to the overlap of the boards but I think it allows some white space and not look too crowded. We got several complements on it the first weekend it was up. Also it was not hard and didn’t take too long to assemble.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 5, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Sturdy, functional bookcase
reviews.reviewText: I was looking for a corner bookcase to fit in a small area, and also be functional for book storage. This one is a perfect fit! The bookcase itself is very sturdy once anchored into the wall. It has plenty of room. For a standard hardcover book. My only qualm is that one shelf had a slight defect on the under side where it screws into the frame. I was unable to completely secure it because of this defect. When I messaged Amazon, the only option would be to return the entire unit for a replacement, they couldn't just send one shelf. Since I had already assembled the whole thing and it was such a small defect I opted to keep the damaged item. It would have been nice to be able to get just the damaged part replaced since it was a small part of the whole thing.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Love the height!
reviews.reviewText: It was hard to find something this tall and the style I wanted. I’m happy with this purchase because it allows me to optimize my styling space. My husband and I put it together in under 10 minutes. The directions are clear and the holes all lined up to fit the screws with no problem.
